{"tid":88730,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"外國升學Design 求指教","createTime":"2017-01-20T19:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T08:50:41.000Z","uid":12045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec71e7253cd91374a3b084b4c4c1bc704d660326","tid":88730,"uid":12045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T19:38:38.000Z","msg":"小弟宜家讀緊yr 2 English major 咩u就 唔講驚自爆<br />\n宜家想完U / Quit U 去讀 visual design/ graphic design <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首要想去日本讀<br />\n其次係<br />\n想報RSA 讀visual communication MA 但又怕入唔到<br />\n<br />\n首選<br />\n日本讀好多選擇，MA感覺上入唔到，4年大又覺得讀完兩個degree會好遲，想早啲出嚟做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n或者係讀專校都好，不過感覺有啲雞<br />\n<br />\n日文就今年先開始讀，所要至少完香港u先可以出發<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n次選<br />\n<br />\n讀degree的話外國大學如果要即時出發我都無所謂 <br />\nMA 都係覺得自己無咁嘅能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d485e3f04b3de1a877ecaa52723651e5310f882","tid":88730,"uid":64071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T20:28:22.000Z","msg":"其實你知唔知香港一年有幾多讀 design 既學生？<br />\n<br />\n做 design 既現實係點，你其實你知唔知嫁？"},{"pid":"ca6906d8fcbb841ea1f393326bb7cd6fc0ca6548","tid":88730,"uid":16275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T20:30:27.000Z","msg":"去日本讀有無日文底？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1632155037996244744aa8fba7821bc69eb86ff6","tid":88730,"uid":12045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T20:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實你知唔知香港一年有幾多讀 design 既學生？<br />\n<br />\n做 design 既現實係點，你其實你知唔知嫁？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無諗過係香港落腳"},{"pid":"7460f6d56c3558ada618bf3478004831f82be5bf","tid":88730,"uid":12045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T20:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去日本讀有無日文底？<img s